Package: ggcovcases
Title: Lineplot Visualisation of COVID-19 Cases and Deaths
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        given = "Shintaro",
        family = "Kinoshita",
        email = "shintaro.kinoshita.584@cranfield.ac.uk",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The ggcovcases package acquires COVID-19 cases or deaths information in each counrty by automatically picking the data from WHO COVID-19 Global Data(https://covid19.who.int/WHO-COVID-19-global-data.csv), and Visualise them as lineplot or connected scatter plot using some ggplot2 functions.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
